b6958d48-c02a-4bfe-b5ed-05f84fe8cb8c.title: Zavistic Rarve
b6958d48-c02a-4bfe-b5ed-05f84fe8cb8c.text:
What are you doing bothering me? Don't you think
some of us have work to do?

ab8b25bc-1be2-4f76-8592-79bc02ea0813.title: <player>
ab8b25bc-1be2-4f76-8592-79bc02ea0813.text: I thought you were here to help?

4d3e9cd6-16d1-49cf-9348-0390817e96ea.title: Zavistic Rarve
4d3e9cd6-16d1-49cf-9348-0390817e96ea.text:
Well... I am, I suppose, anyway... we're very busy
here, hurry up, what do you want?

be425b09-98ac-4ed4-9d19-0f968c8721ab.title: Zavistic Rarve
be425b09-98ac-4ed4-9d19-0f968c8721ab.text:
What are you doing ringing that bell?! Don't you think
some of us have work to do?

e68ded8a-ac35-4160-bcbf-d78d8f04e72d.title: <player>
e68ded8a-ac35-4160-bcbf-d78d8f04e72d.text:
But I was told to ring the bell if I wanted some
attention.

3b54cbfd-3bac-4aa7-8190-d7a704636523.title: Zavistic Rarve
3b54cbfd-3bac-4aa7-8190-d7a704636523.text:
Well...anyway...we're very busy here, hurry up what do
you want?

493aca33-5c93-4670-968c-86dc4ad4a820.title: Zavistic Rarve
493aca33-5c93-4670-968c-86dc4ad4a820.text:
What are you doing...Oh, it's you...sorry...didn't
realise...what can I do for you?

options.text: What is there to do in the Wizards' Guild?
What are the requirements to get in the Wizards' Guild?
What do you do in the Guild?
Ok, thanks.

ac742f43-01dd-4565-b26f-5b6157a895ac.title: <player>
ac742f43-01dd-4565-b26f-5b6157a895ac.text: What is there to do in the Wizards' Guild?

b490e53c-8bec-45bb-bbe4-217960cc8874.title: Zavistic Rarve
b490e53c-8bec-45bb-bbe4-217960cc8874.text:
This is the finest wizards' establishment in the land. We
have magic portals to the other towers of wizardry
around Gielinor. We have a particularly wide collection
of runes in our rune shop. We sell some of the finest

4a1c0a6e-99e3-423c-a9a0-da01bcf4ced6.title: Zavistic Rarve
4a1c0a6e-99e3-423c-a9a0-da01bcf4ced6.text:
mage robes in the land and we have a training area full
of zombies for you to practice your magic on.

6945d5f3-2c72-4475-9c66-7a5affb07253.title: <player>
6945d5f3-2c72-4475-9c66-7a5affb07253.text:
What are the requirements to get in the Wizards'
Guild?

a2244a64-b861-4973-a2ff-454f8d898e33.title: Zavistic Rarve
a2244a64-b861-4973-a2ff-454f8d898e33.text:
You need a magic level of 66, the high magic energy
level is too dangerous for anyone below that level.

7c37f1d3-0097-4ac3-8efc-c5497a347e7e.title: <player>
7c37f1d3-0097-4ac3-8efc-c5497a347e7e.text: What do you do in the Guild?

5201b509-0b08-459c-98b9-e918095b966e.title: Zavistic Rarve
5201b509-0b08-459c-98b9-e918095b966e.text:
I'm the Grand Secretary for the Wizards' Guild, I have
lots of correspondence to keep up with, as well as
attending to the discipline of the more problematic guild
members.

options.text: What is there to do in the Wizards' Guild?
What are the requirements to get in the Wizards' Guild?
What do you do in the Guild?
Can you help me more?

b9023c8f-1151-4b6b-9070-91f105687eff.title: Zavistic Rarve
b9023c8f-1151-4b6b-9070-91f105687eff.text: Bring me a vial and I'll help you a little more.

c6cf4f41-cac8-4514-9668-b4fc575955e3.title: Zavistic Rarve
c6cf4f41-cac8-4514-9668-b4fc575955e3.text: Bring me a vial and I'll help you a little more.

ac7f711c-bb13-4387-bdde-9be53cde8424.title: <player>
ac7f711c-bb13-4387-bdde-9be53cde8424.text: I have a vial here for you.

b1d0f957-d389-40fb-9235-75ad2a530873.title: Zavistic Rarve
b1d0f957-d389-40fb-9235-75ad2a530873.text:
Ok, would you like me to transport you to Port Sarim?
I'm sticking my neck out a bit helping you like this and
can only do it once though!

options.text: Yes, that would be great!
No, I prefer using my legs, thanks all the same.

90ad7bb9-dbba-4dcf-a453-1e02cd17e4b6.title: <player>
90ad7bb9-dbba-4dcf-a453-1e02cd17e4b6.text: No, I prefer using my legs, thanks all the same.

6eafed00-61ef-4d81-99cf-21d0b2fadf0d.text:
Maybe you should have the hand with you before speaking to
Zavistic.

68c604a2-180f-4107-814b-d031b734d923.text: You wave the hand at the wizard.

14289b47-0de4-4064-8e46-67ae08dc9e03.title: <player>
14289b47-0de4-4064-8e46-67ae08dc9e03.text: Ummm... Do you have all your wizards?

81e8ced0-801f-4325-93cf-5c93b8b46925.title: Zavistic Rarve
81e8ced0-801f-4325-93cf-5c93b8b46925.text: All my.... whatever do you mean...?

130530fd-8e01-49a8-aa5f-ea15642510e1.title: <player>
130530fd-8e01-49a8-aa5f-ea15642510e1.text:
The Guard Captain asked me to see if you have any...
missing... wizards.

fab6a491-f104-4e49-9819-5265537e3a38.title: Zavistic Rarve
fab6a491-f104-4e49-9819-5265537e3a38.text: That's silly! No one would kill a wizard... would they?

4823bb17-86d7-411f-98c1-80f717782b34.title: <player>
4823bb17-86d7-411f-98c1-80f717782b34.text:
Well.. maybe, you see Bert found this hand and it
might belong to.. a wizard!

3dcd8ea1-d545-478c-af9d-44b78de57014.title: Zavistic Rarve
3dcd8ea1-d545-478c-af9d-44b78de57014.text:
Bert? Ahh yes, the sandman who seems to have been
working very long hours recently. Let's see that hand...

dea976ac-6e1f-4ee9-85e3-6c92fac628c7.title: Zavistic Rarve
dea976ac-6e1f-4ee9-85e3-6c92fac628c7.text:
Oh my! This is most definitely Clarence, my most able
student! You must find out who did this!

e843d347-a798-44bb-8346-dba8b1d00b9e.title: <player>
e843d347-a798-44bb-8346-dba8b1d00b9e.text: Do you have any input as to the matter at hand?

6f9f8faf-187a-4de0-87e2-e8d85313353e.title: Zavistic Rarve
6f9f8faf-187a-4de0-87e2-e8d85313353e.text:
Well.... Ask Bert about the long hours he's been
working, that sounds suspicious to me. Digging things
up at all hours of the day isn't natural.

e5cbcb69-3db8-42d4-a7db-f91667109fae.title: Zavistic Rarve
e5cbcb69-3db8-42d4-a7db-f91667109fae.text: Did you find out who killed Clarence yet?

fee25e26-b6f3-42e8-95cd-cfa26e36191e.title: <player>
fee25e26-b6f3-42e8-95cd-cfa26e36191e.text: Not yet, but don't lose your head over it.

6f53652e-e56b-4673-b254-229b5e2b2ef1.text:
Perhaps you should have the scroll from Bert with you before you
speak to Zavistic.

b87ae30c-211e-4930-9a72-b94de7e122f3.title: <player>
b87ae30c-211e-4930-9a72-b94de7e122f3.text:
I talked to Bert and found something very strange
about his hours.

701ed11e-1a43-4b09-9904-7463d873fce3.title: <player>
701ed11e-1a43-4b09-9904-7463d873fce3.text:
No, but he doesn't remember changing his hours, and
his rota and the original that his boss Sandy had, are
different!

e09efd8b-30f7-4d02-b54e-49363535f0ef.title: <player>
e09efd8b-30f7-4d02-b54e-49363535f0ef.text:
... oh, and this scroll appeared when they changed - he
gave it to me.

7931a658-6cb5-4f63-8041-04ca862506e2.title: Zavistic Rarve
7931a658-6cb5-4f63-8041-04ca862506e2.text:
I recognise that type of scroll! It's used in a mind
altering spell of some sort. Did you speak to this...
Sandy guy? Perhaps he has a hand in this.

22125d1e-b65e-47d2-aa8f-4f933c2c863e.title: <player>
22125d1e-b65e-47d2-aa8f-4f933c2c863e.text:
I took a look around his office. I don't know about a
hand in it, I think he has both hands and feet in it!

7864cf6c-d346-4c29-88d5-9af063c081b7.title: Zavistic Rarve
7864cf6c-d346-4c29-88d5-9af063c081b7.text:
Even more suspicious! Here, take this magical scrying
orb and get some Truth Serum from Betty in Port
Sarim, she owes me a favour, just tell her I sent you if
she complains.

f84a5b81-7b61-4825-a998-78e7c995d317.title: Zavistic Rarve
f84a5b81-7b61-4825-a998-78e7c995d317.text:
Then you will be equipped to ask Sandy a few
questions. Oh Clarence, I will find your murderer!

07290ed1-23bc-42d3-821f-4370e6b10549.text:
You exchange the scroll for the magical scrying orb.
Perhaps Zavistic can give you even more of a hand to
find the murderer?

options.text: What is there to do in the Wizards' Guild?
What are the requirements to get in the Wizards' Guild?
What do you do in the Guild?
Can you help me more?

082dc637-db99-4e8d-a410-282e8638c4b5.title: Zavistic Rarve
082dc637-db99-4e8d-a410-282e8638c4b5.text: Bring me a vial and I'll help you a little more.

c1a70ec8-7c69-411f-bf84-39a461ad4d0d.title: <player>
c1a70ec8-7c69-411f-bf84-39a461ad4d0d.text: I have a vial here for you.

8cb8abcd-d1f9-4189-898f-e48616da5dcd.title: Zavistic Rarve
8cb8abcd-d1f9-4189-898f-e48616da5dcd.text:
Ok, would you like me to transport you to Port Sarim?
I'm sticking my neck out a bit helping you like this and
can only do it once though!

options.text: Yes, that would be great!
No, I prefer using my legs, thanks all the same.

b928f72f-6ee8-431b-a69c-d6b8dacddfe9.title: <player>
b928f72f-6ee8-431b-a69c-d6b8dacddfe9.text: No, I prefer using my legs, thanks all the same.

options.text: What is there to do in the Wizards' Guild?
What are the requirements to get in the Wizards' Guild?
What do you do in the Guild?
I've lost my magical scrying orb!

a8de9b5e-eafd-4c6c-b71c-da72722f9f6c.title: <player>
a8de9b5e-eafd-4c6c-b71c-da72722f9f6c.text: I've lost my magical scrying orb!

f7bb2182-124e-4b1f-930d-e8ba7b249d49.title: Zavistic Rarve
f7bb2182-124e-4b1f-930d-e8ba7b249d49.text:
No matter, here, have another and please hurry,
whoever killed Clarence must pay!

f79a45d7-aa88-4c36-9061-f527a0116ce0.title: Zavistic Rarve
f79a45d7-aa88-4c36-9061-f527a0116ce0.text: Off you go then, break a leg!

4765e6c1-4204-4ee9-a51a-160bc266dcd7.title: Zavistic Rarve
4765e6c1-4204-4ee9-a51a-160bc266dcd7.text:
Unfortunately I've already helped you with one teleport,
get some exercise - your legs won't fall off!

options.text: What is there to do in the Wizards' Guild?
What are the requirements to get in the Wizards' Guild?
What do you do in the Guild?
I've lost my magical scrying orb!

ff45d2ae-45d3-4f87-bf24-ee5528b759f8.title: <player>
ff45d2ae-45d3-4f87-bf24-ee5528b759f8.text: I've lost my magical scrying orb!

95cbaff1-6da9-44f5-bd0c-7ea9c3f7ba3a.title: Zavistic Rarve
95cbaff1-6da9-44f5-bd0c-7ea9c3f7ba3a.text:
No matter, here, have another and please hurry,
whoever killed Clarence must pay!

7278e685-9ec4-4c67-b826-12680ebb8195.title: <player>
7278e685-9ec4-4c67-b826-12680ebb8195.text: What is there to do in the Wizards' Guild?

e638d5ce-9b73-40d0-9262-43b5078d5c93.title: Zavistic Rarve
e638d5ce-9b73-40d0-9262-43b5078d5c93.text:
This is the finest wizards' establishment in the land. We
have magic portals to the other towers of wizardry
around Gielinor. We have a particularly wide collection
of runes in our rune shop. We sell some of the finest

60d5359e-340f-4c7b-a50f-8b7e6c50950a.title: Zavistic Rarve
60d5359e-340f-4c7b-a50f-8b7e6c50950a.text:
mage robes in the land and we have a training area full
of zombies for you to practice your magic on.

8825d080-b8a2-4ba0-a73c-de9007256dee.title: <player>
8825d080-b8a2-4ba0-a73c-de9007256dee.text:
What are the requirements to get in the Wizards'
Guild?

2d7bb1bb-4f04-433c-b4cf-a93a40ddef7a.title: Zavistic Rarve
2d7bb1bb-4f04-433c-b4cf-a93a40ddef7a.text:
You need a magic level of 66, the high magic energy
level is too dangerous for anyone below that level.

24770b7d-fe63-4f88-a582-8e7dfde9157f.title: <player>
24770b7d-fe63-4f88-a582-8e7dfde9157f.text: What do you do in the Guild?

cab735b0-98c6-40da-b353-ad51824e1522.title: Zavistic Rarve
cab735b0-98c6-40da-b353-ad51824e1522.text:
I'm the Grand Secretary for the Wizards' Guild, I have
lots of correspondence to keep up with, as well as
attending to the discipline of the more problematic guild
members.

1777323c-391b-4c3c-8c6f-fcab72321048.title: Zavistic Rarve
1777323c-391b-4c3c-8c6f-fcab72321048.text: Have you made the serum and talked to Sandy yet?

829de57b-4780-4d3a-8cb3-6c31e8fcdbbf.title: <player>
829de57b-4780-4d3a-8cb3-6c31e8fcdbbf.text: Not yet, but don't bust a gut over it!

d8757e15-900c-4f44-a24d-3c8c119b551f.title: Note
d8757e15-900c-4f44-a24d-3c8c119b551f.text:
Only if they have the orb
Also after putting serum in

options.text: What is there to do in the Wizards' Guild?
What are the requirements to get in the Wizards' Guild?
What do you do in the Guild?
I've lost my magical scrying orb!

85a42d25-9231-4416-869e-2289958c543f.title: <player>
85a42d25-9231-4416-869e-2289958c543f.text: I've lost my magical scrying orb!

baf514a4-6508-4042-ae69-f98762f5664e.title: Zavistic Rarve
baf514a4-6508-4042-ae69-f98762f5664e.text:
No matter, here, have another I've already activated it
for you!

6e061548-52fe-4e09-b46f-f1a2341c133d.title: <player>
6e061548-52fe-4e09-b46f-f1a2341c133d.text: I got the whole story from Sandy... but I lost the orb.

a41b1b85-ece2-426c-95b3-96dc5a7d14ac.title: Zavistic Rarve
a41b1b85-ece2-426c-95b3-96dc5a7d14ac.text:
It's ok, I saw the whole thing as the orb is connected
via magic to me as I enchanted it.

a69a3c5f-959f-4ae3-917a-951c33dc7fbb.title: Zavistic Rarve
a69a3c5f-959f-4ae3-917a-951c33dc7fbb.text:
I think this Sandy needs a lesson, please bring me 5
earth runes and a bucket of sand.

39bc8c85-5808-4e14-9a24-4a21a7046350.title: Zavistic Rarve
39bc8c85-5808-4e14-9a24-4a21a7046350.text:
Don't question me or you'll end up as braindead as that
legless Guard Captain!

ec4087b7-564f-452c-af91-1e7cafe698f9.title: <player>
ec4087b7-564f-452c-af91-1e7cafe698f9.text:
Umm.. ok, I'll get you the 5 earth runes and bucket of
sand.

0fe78d00-b169-4c39-aa9a-69c72819c3f6.text:
You hand the magical scrying orb to the Wizard and watch as the
recording is played back.

1168d7ad-403b-4a32-b466-2e5baad5a682.title: Zavistic Rarve
1168d7ad-403b-4a32-b466-2e5baad5a682.text:
You really mean you forgot? Bring me 5 earth runes
and 1 bucket of sand to help stop that moneygrabbing
Sandy!

9db1082b-33e5-4bc3-838c-cf48fee4e4a3.title: <player>
9db1082b-33e5-4bc3-838c-cf48fee4e4a3.text:
I've brought what you wanted, what are you going to
do?

ecd7a91c-cedb-4767-a887-aa24173a2282.title: Zavistic Rarve
ecd7a91c-cedb-4767-a887-aa24173a2282.text: Ahh excellent, let's have those! Watch and learn...

04e58938-1798-4200-82d9-f6e25e916b2e.text:
The Wizard chants and your attention is taken to the sandpit where
Bert found the hand.

c6e43949-24ef-4382-b6a4-9e4723c61a85.text:
Something very strange happens to the Sandpit, it looks like it has
filled itself up!

9887bbeb-ac47-4fc0-8bc0-526433e77c51.title: Zavistic Rarve
9887bbeb-ac47-4fc0-8bc0-526433e77c51.text:
There, the sand pit will now magically refill. No more
work for Bert!

6d13f57e-e95c-46a9-b1b6-2324294e0160.title: Zavistic Rarve
6d13f57e-e95c-46a9-b1b6-2324294e0160.text:
We must find the rest of Clarence, I've sent some
wizards out to some of the sandpits, would you please
check the Entrana sandpit?

622b8b11-e7a8-4eca-b957-3224f7ec065a.title: Zavistic Rarve
622b8b11-e7a8-4eca-b957-3224f7ec065a.text:
Did you visit the Entrana sandpit yet? Ask the worker
there if he's found an arm or a leg.

ed70f142-3ab7-4edb-9550-020edb86305a.title: <player>
ed70f142-3ab7-4edb-9550-020edb86305a.text:
Not yet no. I've been running around like a headless
chicken, but I'll get to it!

671f2c4c-55c0-49f1-9e30-fea448c9e0ec.text:
Perhaps you should have the wizard's head with you before speaking
to Zavistic.

d6f23c3a-0248-473b-81a4-5a8fa404ca95.text: You show the wizard the head.

2e16e0fb-d85a-4f85-8907-66f7d27796d6.title: Zavistic Rarve
2e16e0fb-d85a-4f85-8907-66f7d27796d6.text: Alas poor Clarence. I knew him, <player>.

9d77cb28-fb3f-4627-b6ab-b75262ab623d.title: Zavistic Rarve
9d77cb28-fb3f-4627-b6ab-b75262ab623d.text:
Thank you - we shall bury him today. I have sent word
for the guards to arrest Sandy, so no one will ever see
him again!

925e4cc6-1caa-4aa4-8550-dd5d82353d5e.title: Zavistic Rarve
925e4cc6-1caa-4aa4-8550-dd5d82353d5e.text:
Thank you so much for helping to lay Clarence to rest
and lock up his murderer!
